text: lokkhan nei thansuokr delke ban sanyea champoh banda anak del kaotakhlach a l laoh noh ku mean t ne l cheachraen haur pi kraom vea del phleanouphl ning mlob robsa vea mean chea rieng rhaut . noh kuchea lotthophl chongokraoy samreab banda anak del kaotakhlach a l laoh . rie lotthophl chongokraoy robsa puok del brachheang noh ku nork
